company.name: SERTECPET®
company.description:
SERTECPET® is a multinational  company specialized in providing worldwide Integrated Energy Solutions with state-of-the-art technology. 

We cater to oil and gas field services, including integrated evaluation and production services for wells with hydraulic pumping. We possess the necessary technology to determine the real production potential and operating parameters, so as to recommend the best strategies to optimize well production.
